title: High school football: Wheaton North closes season with win
text:
High school football: Wheaton North closes season with win   1:11 a.m. CDT By SUBURBAN LIFE MEDIA 
WHEATON â€“ The playoffs weren't in the cards for Wheaton North's football team, but the Falcons capped the regular season with a 9-7 win against a solid Waubonsie Valley team on Oct. 23. 
North finished the season with a 4-5 record that included a three-game winning streak against Naperville North, Metea Valley and Lake Park. The Falcons were 4-4 in the DuPage Valley Conference.
